                      "code": "\tdropdown \u003d self.parent.getChild(\"Toolbar\").getChild(\"DatasetModeDropdown\")\n\tvalue \u003d dropdown.props.value\n\tparts \u003d str(value or \"all\").rsplit(\":\", 1)\n\tmode \u003d parts[-1] if parts else \"all\"\n\tpathByMode \u003d {\n\t\t\"all\": \"[Otto_FleetManager]MainControl/Runtime/HttpHistory\",\n\t\t\"get\": \"[Otto_FleetManager]MainControl/Runtime/HttpGetHistory\",\n\t\t\"post\": \"[Otto_FleetManager]MainControl/Runtime/HttpPostHistory\"\n\t}\n\ttagPath \u003d pathByMode.get(str(mode).lower(), pathByMode[\"all\"])\n\tdatasetValue \u003d system.tag.readBlocking([tagPath])[0].value\n\tif self.props.UpdateTable or self.props.data is None:\n\t\tself.props.UpdateTable \u003d False\n\t\tif datasetValue is None:\n\t\t\treturn system.dataset.toDataSet([\"Ts\", \"Method\", \"Url\", \"Request\", \"Response\", \"Ok\", \"DurationMs\", \"Error\"], [])\n\t\ttry:\n\t\t\treturn system.dataset.sort(datasetValue, \"Ts\", True)\n\t\texcept Exception:\n\t\t\treturn datasetValue\n\treturn self.props.data",
